[{"title":"Basic MarkDown Grammar","url":"/2020/12/30/Basic%20Markdown/","content":"<h3 id=\"Intro\"><a href=\"#Intro\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Intro\"></a>Intro</h3><p>Since most posts of my blog are wriiten by Markdown, I will take down some basic Markdown grammar. Hope this can help you learn more about Markdown. </p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<br/>\n\n<h3 id=\"What-is-Markdown\"><a href=\"#What-is-Markdown\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"What is Markdown?\"></a>What is Markdown?</h3><blockquote>\n<p>Markdown is a lightweight markup language for creating formatted text using a plain-text editor. John Gruber and Aaron Swartz created Markdown in 2004 as a markup language that is appealing to the human users in its source form. Markdown is widely used in blogging, instant messaging, online forums, collaboration software, documentation pages, and even readme files.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p align=\"right\">---Wikipedia</p>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"Grammar\"><a href=\"#Grammar\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Grammar\"></a>Grammar</h3><h4 id=\"Heading\"><a href=\"#Heading\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Heading\"></a>Heading</h4><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\"># H1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">## H2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">### H3</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">#### H4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">##### H5</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">###### H6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"Bold\"><a href=\"#Bold\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Bold\"></a>Bold</h4><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"strong\">**bold text**</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"Italic\"><a href=\"#Italic\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Italic\"></a>Italic</h4><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"emphasis\">*italicized text*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"Blockquote\"><a href=\"#Blockquote\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Blockquote\"></a>Blockquote</h4><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"quote\">&gt; blockquote</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"Code\"><a href=\"#Code\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Code\"></a>Code</h4><p>``` javascript<br>var canvas = document.getElementById(“canvas”);<br>var context = canvas.getContext(“2d”);<br>```</p>\n<p>i.e. Markdown will render this code with ‘javascript’ grammar.<br>effect:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> canvas = <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"string\">&quot;canvas&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> context = canvas.getContext(<span class=\"string\">&quot;2d&quot;</span>); </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"Link\"><a href=\"#Link\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Link\"></a>Link</h4><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">title</span>](<span class=\"link\">https://www.example.com</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>effect:<br><a href=\"https://www.darklyh.com/\">Home</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"Horizontal-Line\"><a href=\"#Horizontal-Line\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Horizontal Line\"></a>Horizontal Line</h4><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>effect:</p>\n\n<hr>\n</br>\nWhat's more, Markdown support HTML5 grammar. This means you can use &ltbr&gt and other grammars in HTML5.\n","categories":["Computer Science"],"tags":["Markdown","Tutorial"]},{"title":"Blue Screen 404 Page","url":"/2021/01/05/Blue-Screen-404-Page/","content":"<h3 id=\"Intro\"><a href=\"#Intro\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Intro\"></a>Intro</h3><p>The website hosting server will typically generate a “404 Not Found” web page when a user attempts to follow a broken or dead link; hence an good 404 page is important for the blog. Here I’m going to share a Microsoft Blue Screen style 404 page.<br><img src=\"/images/404effect.jpg\" alt=\"effect\"></p>\n<center>(Effect Picture)</center>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<br>\n\n<h3 id=\"Source-Code\"><a href=\"#Source-Code\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Source Code\"></a>Source Code</h3><p>Here is H5 source code.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"meta-keyword\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">charset</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">http-equiv</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">content</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;IE=edge&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;viewport&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">content</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span>404 - Page Not Found<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            body &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">                <span class=\"selector-tag\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"selector-id\">#0099CC</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">                <span class=\"selector-tag\">color</span>: <span class=\"selector-id\">#FFFFFF</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,  sans-serif;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                margin-left: 100px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">            <span class=\"selector-class\">.face</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                font-size: 100px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            p &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                font-size: 24px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                padding: 8px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                line-height: 40px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">            <span class=\"selector-class\">.tips</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                font-size: 16px</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">            <span class=\"comment\">/*Optimization for small screen*/</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">            <span class=\"keyword\">@media</span> screen <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> (<span class=\"attribute\">max-width:</span> <span class=\"number\">600px</span>) &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                body &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    margin: 0 10px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                p &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    font-size: 18px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    line-height: 30px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">                <span class=\"selector-class\">.tips</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                    display: inline-block;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    padding-top: 10px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    font-size: 14px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    line-height: 20px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">            <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> i = <span class=\"number\">10</span>; <span class=\"comment\">//countdown in 10 seconds</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">            <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> intervalid;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">            intervalid = <span class=\"built_in\">setInterval</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;countdown()&quot;</span>, <span class=\"number\">1000</span>);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">            <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">countdown</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (i == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">                    javascript :history.back(-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)<span class=\"comment\">// Default: go to the previous page</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">                    <span class=\"comment\">//window.location.href = &quot;https://darklyh.com&quot;; //you can also decide to redirect to which page</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">                    <span class=\"built_in\">clearInterval</span>(intervalid);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">                <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"string\">&quot;mes&quot;</span>).innerHTML = i;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                i--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">            <span class=\"built_in\">window</span>.onload = countdown;    <span class=\"comment\">// countdown starts as the page is loaded</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;face&quot;</span>&gt;</span>:)<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>404 Page Not Found :</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>You ran into a Black Hole where there is nothing.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;tips&quot;</span>&gt;</span>If you&#x27;d like to know more, you can email luo_yihang@outlook to blame Luo Yihang.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            After <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;mes&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span> seconds, we will help you automatically return to the previous page.<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>You can click <a href=\"http://www.darklyh.com/404.html\">here</a> to visist this 404 page.</p>\n<h3 id=\"How-to-put-404-page-on-Your-Web\"><a href=\"#How-to-put-404-page-on-Your-Web\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"How to put 404 page on Your Web\"></a>How to put 404 page on Your Web</h3><ol>\n<li>Create 404.html in your web root directory and define the content as you like;(Now you can visist 404 page at yourdomain/404.html, but you cannot visist 404 page while you access to a dead or nonexistent link.)</li>\n<li>Follow your service provider rules to set 404 page.</li>\n</ol>\n","categories":["Computer Science"],"tags":["HTML5","Web Construction"]}]